Sentencas: Yttria-stabilised zirconia (YSZ) electrolyte films for solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) applications were prepared by reactive DC sputtering.
Titulo: Influence of electrode contacts on conductivity measurements of thin YSZ electrolyte films and the impact on solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The films of 3-9 mum in thickness were deposited onto NiO/YSZ composite anodes.
Titulo: Influence of electrode contacts on conductivity measurements of thin YSZ electrolyte films and the impact on solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The conductivity of the electrolyte films was determined by impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Influence of electrode contacts on conductivity measurements of thin YSZ electrolyte films and the impact on solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The measured conductivity was low compared to the conductivity of the thick YSZ substrates or bulk material previously reported.
Titulo: Influence of electrode contacts on conductivity measurements of thin YSZ electrolyte films and the impact on solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The low conductivity of the thin films is explained as an artefact of the contacting electrodes during measurement and not of the deposited films themselves.
Titulo: Influence of electrode contacts on conductivity measurements of thin YSZ electrolyte films and the impact on solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: An estimation of the influence of the contacting electrodes in fuel cell operation on the conductivity of the solid electrolyte is made.
Titulo: Influence of electrode contacts on conductivity measurements of thin YSZ electrolyte films and the impact on solid oxide fuel cells
